procstep.procdesc: oregon_scenic_byways was created using data from three sources. State owned portions are represented by the Integrated Transportation Information System (ITIS), Non State functionally classed segments by HGIS15 and local roads by OR-TRANS. Mile points were identified and dynamic segmentation was performed. The resulting shapefiles were exported out of GeoMedia 6.0. The files were merged and fields manipulated to Oregon Department of Transportation (ODOT) spatial data attribute standards using ArcGIS 9.2
